name: Ortugg
Lore: 'Gamorrean in charge of the Gamorreans at Jabba''s palace. Posted to stand guard at the entrance cavern. Assigned by Jabba to keep an eye on Tessek.',
Text: 'Deploys only on Tatooine. Functions as a leader if present with another Gamorrean. While at Audience Chamber, all your other Gamorreans are forfeit +2.',
